title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-19-2013 TUES
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-19-2013 TUES



Tuesday, November 19, 2013



Dick Morris On Hillary's Credentials.

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. NFL running back has his dreadlocks ripped out by the roots during tackle.

2. Mike presents transcript of Obamacare testimony from 4 years ago showing 
    the administration was questioned by Republicans during hearing about 
      the ability to keep private medical insurance under the plan.




 - 10AM hour

1. Guest: Fred Wszolek, Spokesman for the Workforce Fairness Institute

    NLRB Warning Shot to Walmart.

2. Douglas County school district students protest results of school board election.




 - 11AM hour

1. More discussion of teacher unions. 

2. Father called unfit for refusing to take his 4 year old to McDonalds.

3. Oxford Dictionary word of the year is "selfie."

4. Dick Morris disputes Bill Clinton's assessment of Hillary's credentials.
